commit.message: Format the JSON for D3 visualisation
Add reset endpoint to server (to clear entities on GET)
Add ability to keep POSTing words to ML server
Fix formatting of JSON string output
Server returns a json object using Language API

Fix import issue for google cloud language

This is because App Engine standard doesn't support Google Cloud in Python 2 - see googleapis/google-cloud-python README
Cleaned up, fixed bug, styling improvements.
